creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml: At Chapel Hill Training, private personal training takes on a customized and focused approach, uniquely designed based on the goals of each individual client. Our certified expert trainers have worked with clients rehabbing from injury, working towards a fitness goal, or beginning a workout regimen. Our uniquely tailored approach is unlike anything you will have experienced before. We will ensure that you are getting an excellent training session with education, form refinement, and a well-rounded approach. We will challenge you to get better with each and every workout. With the Chapel Hill Training App, you can start tracking your workouts and meals, measuring results, and achieving your fitness goals on your own schedule, all with the help of your trusted CHT personal trainer. Download the app today! And be sure to check out our website at: www.chapelhilltraining.com or our social media pages @chapelhilltraining for Facebook and Instagram.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Consistency is key with this release! Introducing habit streaks and achievement badges—a new way to motivate clients to build healthy habits! Clients can create habit winning streaks by completing a habit every day that it’s scheduled into their calendars. As their streak continues to grow, they'll unlock special achievement badges at various milestones. 

As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
As much as we’d all like, big changes unfortunately don’t happen overnight. That’s why we’ve introduced habit coaching—a new way to help clients make small, sustainable lifestyle changes! Trainers can now create habits within our Master Habit Library and prescribe them to clients. As clients complete habits each day, they will earn habit streaks and unlock special achievement badges over time.
As always, we’ve also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.

We’ve made some exciting upgrades to the Apple Watch App powered by Trainerize that will make it easier for clients to train on the go! Now, clients can leave their phones behind and be able to start and track any workout (regular, circuit, and interval), including three new cardio activities, swimming, dancing, and HIIT, directly from their watch!
As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
